{"title":"APM Hostname Config Audit","description":"Use this dashboard to examine potential hostname configuration issues. You can see if any of your services has hostnames that seem to resemble podnames or services that are emitting empty hostnames. Both of these issues might impact your product experience and can be resolved with proper configuration.","widgets":[{"id":8573572782389341,"definition":{"type":"note","content":"This is a dashboard to examine potential host configuration issues. You can see if any of your services has hostnames that seem to resemble pod names, or services that are emitting empty hostnames. While empty hostnames may be intentional in some configurations, unexpected empty values could impact your product experience. You can also verify whether the tracer host reported matches the host resolved by Datadog. Use this view to confirm whether these patterns are expected or need attention.\n\nProper hostname configuration depends on your set up. To learn how to configure hostnames properly with OpenTelemetry, check out [this documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/opentelemetry/config/hostname_tagging/?tab=host). To learn how to configure hostnames with Agent check out [this documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/agent/troubleshooting/hostname_containers/?tab=datadogoperator).","background_color":"white","font_size":"14","text_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","show_tick":false,"tick_pos":"50%","tick_edge":"left","has_padding":true},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":12,"height":2}},{"id":2292956402325562,"definition":{"title":"Pod like hostnames (hostnames that look like podnames, likely misconfigured)","show_title":true,"type":"group","layout_type":"ordered","widgets":[{"id":2712225072112407,"definition":{"title":"Total affected spans ","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"query_value","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env,$service,issue_type:pod_like_hostname}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar"}],"autoscale":true,"precision":2,"timeseries_background":{"type":"area"}},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":2282531114052878,"definition":{"title":"Services generating hostnames that look like pods","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"toplist","requests":[{"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env AND (issue_type:pod_like_hostname)} by {service}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar","formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"sort":{"count":10,"order_by":[{"type":"formula","index":0,"order":"desc"}]}}],"style":{"display":{"type":"stacked","legend":"automatic"}}},"layout":{"x":6,"y":0,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":1477835871208479,"definition":{"title":"Breakdown of hostnames that look like pods","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"query_table","requests":[{"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env AND (issue_type:pod_like_hostname)} by {service,env}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar","sort":{"count":10,"order_by":[{"type":"formula","index":0,"order":"desc"}]},"formulas":[{"cell_display_mode":"bar","formula":"query1"}]}],"has_search_bar":"auto"},"layout":{"x":0,"y":3,"width":12,"height":4}}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":2,"width":12,"height":8}},{"id":3517038316079138,"definition":{"title":"Empty hostnames (likely misconfigured)","show_title":true,"type":"group","layout_type":"ordered","widgets":[{"id":4302529319173068,"definition":{"title":"Total affected spans ","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"query_value","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env,$service,issue_type:empty_hostname}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar"}],"autoscale":true,"precision":2,"timeseries_background":{"type":"area"}},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":7313851251156465,"definition":{"title":"Services generating empty hostnames ","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"toplist","requests":[{"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env AND (issue_type:empty_hostname)} by {service}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar","formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"sort":{"count":10,"order_by":[{"type":"formula","index":0,"order":"desc"}]}}],"style":{"display":{"type":"stacked","legend":"automatic"}}},"layout":{"x":6,"y":0,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":7815894061585333,"definition":{"title":"Breakdown of services emitting empty hostnames","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","type":"query_table","requests":[{"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:datadog.apm.hostname_issue{$env AND (issue_type:empty_hostname)} by {service,env}.weighted()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar","sort":{"count":10,"order_by":[{"type":"formula","index":0,"order":"desc"}]},"formulas":[{"cell_display_mode":"bar","formula":"query1"}]}],"has_search_bar":"auto"},"layout":{"x":0,"y":3,"width":12,"height":4}}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":20,"width":12,"height":8,"is_column_break":true}},{"id":6182947305716253,"definition":{"title":"Tracer Hostname Match Rate Analysis","show_title":true,"type":"group","layout_type":"ordered","widgets":[{"id":3857291046382719,"definition":{"type":"note","content":"This graph shows how often the hostname reported by your tracer matches the host Datadog resolves for the trace. A consistently low or declining rate can indicate that traces are arriving with a hostname that differs from the host where your application actually runs. This can happen when traces are routed through an OpenTelemetry Collector or a shared gateway. This can affect host-based correlation and host counts. If you have concerns, reach out to our product team for assistance.","background_color":"white","font_size":"12","text_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","show_tick":false,"has_padding":true},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":3,"height":3}},{"id":7203948571629384,"definition":{"title":"Hostname Match Rate %","type":"query_value","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"equal / (equal + not_equal) * 100"}],"queries":[{"name":"equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_equal{*}.as_count()","aggregator":"sum"},{"name":"not_equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_not_equal{*}.as_count()","aggregator":"sum"}],"response_format":"scalar"}],"autoscale":false,"custom_unit":"%","precision":2,"timeseries_background":{"type":"area"}},"layout":{"x":3,"y":0,"width":3,"height":3}},{"id":4958371620483951,"definition":{"title":"Hostname Equal vs Not Equal (spans/s)","show_legend":true,"legend_layout":"horizontal","type":"timeseries","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"equal","alias":"Hostname Equal"},{"formula":"not_equal","alias":"Hostname Not Equal"}],"queries":[{"name":"equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_equal{*}"},{"name":"not_equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_not_equal{*}"}],"response_format":"timeseries","style":{"palette":"classic"},"display_type":"bars"}]},"layout":{"x":6,"y":0,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":1629384057193847,"definition":{"title":"Tracer Hostname Match Rate % over time","show_legend":true,"type":"timeseries","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"equal / (equal + not_equal) * 100","alias":"Match Rate %"}],"queries":[{"name":"equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_equal{*}"},{"name":"not_equal","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:logs.processing.spans_data_reporter.tracer_hostname_not_equal{*}"}],"response_format":"timeseries","style":{"palette":"classic","line_type":"solid","line_width":"normal"},"display_type":"line"}],"yaxis":{"min":"0","max":"100"}},"layout":{"x":0,"y":3,"width":12,"height":3}}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":28,"width":12,"height":7}}],"template_variables":[{"name":"env","prefix":"env","available_values":[],"default":"*"},{"name":"service","prefix":"service","available_values":[],"default":"*"}],"layout_type":"ordered","notify_list":[],"reflow_type":"fixed"}